data.title: Disappointed, Food was Average, Expected More
data.text: Ordered this one night while I was at work. I got the gyro plate, with rice, and pita bread. When I got my food, everything was cooked well. Although I was surprised that the gyro meat was a slab and sliced like a steak and not like at other greek cafe's/restaurants, where it is cut up. The meat didn't seem to be seasoned as well either. Overall I was disappointed and was expecting more. Service was nice that they delivered, and they were nice on the phone, but the food was not what I was expecting.
